    <title>【SICP】 test_3_23</title>
    <url>/p/d9efbaf4.html</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="问题描述："><a href="#问题描述：" class="headerlink" title="问题描述："></a>问题描述：</h2><ul>
<li>用序列实现双端队列 deque ，即可从前或从后插入或删除。<ul>
<li>构造函数 <code>make_deque</code> ;</li>
<li>选择函数 <code>front_deque</code> 、 <code>rear_deque</code> ;</li>
<li>改变函数 <code>front_isnert_deque!</code> 、<code>rear_insert_deque!</code> 、<code>front_delete_deque!</code> 、<code>rear_delete_deque!</code> 。</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>要求是所有操作都需要在 <code>O(1)</code> 步骤内完成。</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="解题思路："><a href="#解题思路：" class="headerlink" title="解题思路："></a>解题思路：</h2><ul>
<li><p>SIPC 3.3.2 实现了队列 queue ，其为链表实现，队列的链表节点包括 data 指针和 next 指针：<img src="/p/d9efbaf4/SICP_queue.jpg" alt="SICP_queue"></p>
</li>
<li><p>所以不难想象出要实现双端队列，其节点需要三个指针，包括 data 指针、next 指针和 last 指针：<img src="/p/d9efbaf4/SICP_deque.jpg" alt="SICP_deque"></p>
</li>
<li><p>有了前面序列实现双端队列节点的假设之后，其他操作都比较容易推导写出，但这里还存在一个问题，即需要重现实现 deque 的打印。</p>
<ul>
<li>要注意的是，为了结果展示，在所有改变函数中最后都会返回打印结果，但原改变操作仍然是 <code>O(1)</code> 时间内完成的。</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="代码实现："><a href="#代码实现：" class="headerlink" title="代码实现："></a>代码实现：</h2><figure class="highlight scheme"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">;; 已跑通，但很多冗余代码</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">;; 制造一个双端节点</span></span><br><span class="line">(<span class="name"><span class="built_in">define</span></span> (<span class="name">node</span>) (<span class="name"><span class="built_in">cons</span></span> nil (<span class="name"><span class="built_in">cons</span></span> nil nil)))</span><br><span class="line">(<span class="name"><span class="built_in">define</span></span> (<span class="name">set_node_val!</span> n x) (<span class="name"><span class="built_in">set-car!</span></span> n x))</span><br><span class="line">(<span class="name"><span class="built_in">define</span></span> (<span class="name">last_ptr</span> n) (<span class="name"><span class="built_in">cadr</span></span> n)) <span class="comment">;; 当前节点的前一个</span></span><br><span class="line">(<span class="name"><span class="built_in">define</span></span> (<span class="name">next_ptr</span> n) (<span class="name">cddr</span> n)) <span class="comment">;; 当前节点的下一个</span></span><br><span class="line">(<span class="name"><span class="built_in">define</span></span> (<span class="name">connect_two_node</span> nl nr)</span><br><span class="line">  (<span class="name"><span class="built_in">begin</span></span> (<span class="name"><span class="built_in">set-car!</span></span> (<span class="name"><span class="built_in">cdr</span></span> nr) nl)</span><br><span class="line">         (<span class="name"><span class="built_in">set-cdr!</span></span> (<span class="name"><span class="built_in">cdr</span></span> nl) nr)</span><br><span class="line">         <span class="symbol">&#x27;OK</span>))</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">(<span class="name"><span class="built_in">define</span></span> (<span class="name">make_deque</span>) (<span class="name"><span class="built_in">cons</span></span> nil nil))</span><br><span class="line">(<span class="name"><span class="built_in">define</span></span> (<span class="name">front_ptr</span> d) (<span class="name"><span class="built_in">car</span></span> d))</span><br><span class="line">(<span class="name"><span class="built_in">define</span></span> (<span class="name">rear_ptr</span> d) (<span class="name"><span class="built_in">cdr</span></span> d))</span><br><span class="line">(<span class="name"><span class="built_in">define</span></span> (<span class="name">set_front_ptr!</span> d n) (<span class="name"><span class="built_in">set-car!</span></span> d n))</span><br><span class="line">(<span class="name"><span class="built_in">define</span></span> (<span class="name">set_rear_ptr!</span> d n) (<span class="name"><span class="built_in">set-cdr!</span></span> d n))</span><br><span class="line">(<span class="name"><span class="built_in">define</span></span> (<span class="name">empty_deque?</span> d)</span><br><span class="line">  (<span class="name"><span class="built_in">or</span></span> (<span class="name"><span class="built_in">null?</span></span> (<span class="name">front_ptr</span> d)) (<span class="name"><span class="built_in">null?</span></span> (<span class="name">rear_ptr</span> d))))</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">(<span class="name"><span class="built_in">define</span></span> (<span class="name">clear_deque</span> d)</span><br><span class="line">  (<span class="name"><span class="built_in">begin</span></span> (<span class="name"><span class="built_in">set-car!</span></span> d nil)</span><br><span class="line">         (<span class="name"><span class="built_in">set-cdr!</span></span> d nil)</span><br><span class="line">         <span class="symbol">&#x27;OK</span>))</span><br><span class="line">(<span class="name"><span class="built_in">define</span></span> (<span class="name">insert_one_element!</span> d x)</span><br><span class="line">  (<span class="name"><span class="built_in">let</span></span> ((<span class="name">new_node</span> (<span class="name">node</span>)))</span><br><span class="line">    (<span class="name"><span class="built_in">begin</span></span> (<span class="name">set_front_ptr!</span> d new_node)</span><br><span class="line">           (<span class="name">set_rear_ptr!</span> d new_node)</span><br><span class="line">           (<span class="name">set_node_val!</span> new_node x)</span><br><span class="line">           <span class="symbol">&#x27;OK</span>)))</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">(<span class="name"><span class="built_in">define</span></span> (<span class="name">front_insert_deque!</span> d x)</span><br><span class="line">  (<span class="name"><span class="built_in">cond</span></span> ((<span class="name">empty_deque?</span> d)</span><br><span class="line">         (<span class="name"><span class="built_in">begin</span></span> (<span class="name">clear_deque</span> d)</span><br><span class="line">                (<span class="name">insert_one_element!</span> d x)</span><br><span class="line">                (<span class="name">print_deque</span> d)))</span><br><span class="line">        (<span class="name"><span class="built_in">else</span></span></span><br><span class="line">         (<span class="name"><span class="built_in">let</span></span> ((<span class="name">new_node</span> (<span class="name">node</span>)))</span><br><span class="line">           (<span class="name"><span class="built_in">begin</span></span> (<span class="name">set_node_val!</span> new_node x)</span><br><span class="line">                  (<span class="name">connect_two_node</span> new_node (<span class="name">front_ptr</span> d))</span><br><span class="line">                  (<span class="name">set_front_ptr!</span> d new_node)</span><br><span class="line">                  (<span class="name">print_deque</span> d))))))</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">(<span class="name"><span class="built_in">define</span></span> (<span class="name">rear_insert_deque!</span> d x)</span><br><span class="line">  (<span class="name"><span class="built_in">cond</span></span> ((<span class="name">empty_deque?</span> d)</span><br><span class="line">         (<span class="name"><span class="built_in">begin</span></span> (<span class="name">clear_deque</span> d)</span><br><span class="line">                (<span class="name">insert_one_element!</span> d x)</span><br><span class="line">                (<span class="name">print_deque</span> d)))</span><br><span class="line">        (<span class="name"><span class="built_in">else</span></span></span><br><span class="line">         (<span class="name"><span class="built_in">let</span></span> ((<span class="name">new_node</span> (<span class="name">node</span>)))</span><br><span class="line">           (<span class="name"><span class="built_in">begin</span></span> (<span class="name">set_node_val!</span> new_node x)</span><br><span class="line">                  (<span class="name">connect_two_node</span> (<span class="name">rear_ptr</span> d) new_node)</span><br><span class="line">                  (<span class="name">set_rear_ptr!</span> d new_node)</span><br><span class="line">                  (<span class="name">print_deque</span> d))))))</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">(<span class="name"><span class="built_in">define</span></span> (<span class="name">front_delete_deque!</span> d)</span><br><span class="line">  (<span class="name"><span class="built_in">cond</span></span> ((<span class="name">empty_deque?</span> d) (<span class="name">error</span> <span class="string">&quot;delete error&quot;</span>))</span><br><span class="line">        ((<span class="name"><span class="built_in">eq?</span></span> (<span class="name">front_ptr</span> d) (<span class="name">rear_ptr</span> d)) (<span class="name"><span class="built_in">begin</span></span> (<span class="name">clear_deque</span> d)</span><br><span class="line">                                                 (<span class="name">print_deque</span> d)))</span><br><span class="line">        (<span class="name"><span class="built_in">else</span></span></span><br><span class="line">         (<span class="name"><span class="built_in">begin</span></span> (<span class="name">set_front_ptr!</span> d (<span class="name">next_ptr</span> (<span class="name">front_ptr</span> d)))</span><br><span class="line">                (<span class="name"><span class="built_in">set-car!</span></span> (<span class="name"><span class="built_in">cdr</span></span> (<span class="name">front_ptr</span> d)) nil)</span><br><span class="line">                (<span class="name">print_deque</span> d)))))</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">(<span class="name"><span class="built_in">define</span></span> (<span class="name">rear_delete_deque!</span> d)</span><br><span class="line">  (<span class="name"><span class="built_in">cond</span></span> ((<span class="name">empty_deque?</span> d) (<span class="name">error</span> <span class="string">&quot;delete error&quot;</span>))</span><br><span class="line">        ((<span class="name"><span class="built_in">eq?</span></span> (<span class="name">front_ptr</span> d) (<span class="name">rear_ptr</span> d)) (<span class="name"><span class="built_in">begin</span></span> (<span class="name">clear_deque</span> d)</span><br><span class="line">                                                 (<span class="name">print_deque</span> d)))</span><br><span class="line">        (<span class="name"><span class="built_in">else</span></span></span><br><span class="line">         (<span class="name"><span class="built_in">begin</span></span> (<span class="name">set_rear_ptr!</span> d (<span class="name">last_ptr</span> (<span class="name">rear_ptr</span> d)))</span><br><span class="line">                (<span class="name"><span class="built_in">set-cdr!</span></span> (<span class="name"><span class="built_in">cdr</span></span> (<span class="name">rear_ptr</span> d)) nil)</span><br><span class="line">                (<span class="name">print_deque</span> d)))))</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">(<span class="name"><span class="built_in">define</span></span> (<span class="name">print_deque</span> d)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  (<span class="name"><span class="built_in">define</span></span> a (<span class="name">front_ptr</span> d))</span><br><span class="line">  (<span class="name"><span class="built_in">define</span></span> b (<span class="name">rear_ptr</span> d))</span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">  (<span class="name"><span class="built_in">define</span></span> (<span class="name">iter</span> ptr)</span><br><span class="line">    (<span class="name"><span class="built_in">if</span></span> (<span class="name"><span class="built_in">null?</span></span> ptr)</span><br><span class="line">        nil</span><br><span class="line">        (<span class="name"><span class="built_in">cons</span></span> (<span class="name"><span class="built_in">car</span></span> ptr) (<span class="name">iter</span> (<span class="name">next_ptr</span> ptr)))))</span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">  (<span class="name">iter</span> a))</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">(<span class="name"><span class="built_in">define</span></span> d (<span class="name">make_deque</span>))</span><br><span class="line">d</span><br><span class="line">(<span class="name">rear_insert_deque!</span> d <span class="symbol">&#x27;a</span>)</span><br><span class="line">(<span class="name">rear_insert_deque!</span> d <span class="symbol">&#x27;b</span>)</span><br><span class="line">(<span class="name">rear_insert_deque!</span> d <span class="symbol">&#x27;c</span>)</span><br><span class="line">(<span class="name">front_insert_deque!</span> d <span class="symbol">&#x27;d</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">(<span class="name">front_delete_deque!</span> d)</span><br><span class="line">(<span class="name">rear_delete_deque!</span> d)</span><br><span class="line">(<span class="name">front_delete_deque!</span> d)</span><br><span class="line">(<span class="name">empty_deque?</span> d)</span><br><span class="line">(<span class="name">rear_delete_deque!</span> d)</span><br><span class="line">(<span class="name">empty_deque?</span> d)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
